node.text:
Finally! Safari Bowling Set is here!!! Yay 😊
It is a good activity to build gross and fine motor skills, also social play.
. 
Safari Bowling Set by BeginAgain (@milknplay.sg) is made of eco-friendly materials, promote well-balanced play, fine and gross motor skills, and cognitive functions.
.
BeginAgain toys are modeled from 5  fundamental types of activity into their play: artist, writer, inventor, sportster, and hero. All of these principles are crucial to promote balanced approach development of a child.
.
Check out other toys from BeginAgain at @milknplay.sg and use promo code "maxwell15" for 15% off till end of October 2020. Don’t miss it!

Ps: Maxwell loves to play with dog family colour puzzle 😊
Thank you for sharing mummy! Loves to see Maxwell play!❤️
